<statement>
<p>Solve this system of equations using substitution.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}-{5}{y}={30}</m> </p>
<p>
  <m>\displaystyle{8}{x}-{y}=-{41}</m></p>
<p><fillin characters="8" /></p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li><m>\displaystyle{\left(-{5},{1}\right)}</m></li></ul></p><p>We chose (for no special reason) to solve the first equation for <m>\displaystyle{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+-{5}{y}={30}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}={30}-{\left(-{5}{y}\right)}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=\frac{{{30}-{\left(-{5}{y}\right)}}}{{-{{7}}}}</m></p>
<p>Then we can substitute this into the second equation.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{8}{\left(\frac{{{30}-{\left(-{5}{y}\right)}}}{{-{{7}}}}\right)}+-{1}{y}=-{41}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle\frac{{8}}{{-{{7}}}}\cdot{\left({30}\right)}-\frac{{8}}{{-{{7}}}}{\left(-{5}\right)}{y}+-{1}{y}=-{41}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{34.285714285714}-{\left(-{5.7142857142857}\right)}{y}+-{1}{y}=-{41}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{5.7142857142857}{y}+{\left(-{1}\right)}{y}=-{41}--{34.285714285714}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{5.7142857142857}{y}+{\left(-{1}\right)}{y}=-{6.7142857142857}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{\left(-{5.7142857142857}+{\left(-{1}\right)}\right)}{y}=-{6.7142857142857}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{6.7142857142857}{y}=-{6.7142857142857}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{y}=-\frac{{6.7142857142857}}{{-{{6.7142857142857}}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{y}={1}</m></p>
<p>Finally we can substitute this y value into the first equation to solve for x.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+-{5}{\left({1}\right)}={30}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+{\left(-{5}\right)}={30}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}={30}-{\left(-{5}\right)}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}={35}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=\frac{{35}}{{-{{7}}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-{5}</m></p>
<p>Thus the answer is <m>\displaystyle{\left(-{5},{1}\right)}</m>.</p>

</solution>
</myopenmath>

